fields.calculatedFormula:
"|" /***** QUARTER OFFSET CALCULATION *****/
&
TEXT(
    CEILING(MONTH(Close_Date__c) / 3) - CEILING(MONTH(TODAY()) / 3)
    +
    4 * (YEAR(Close_Date__c) - YEAR(TODAY()))
)
&
"Q"
& /***** QUARTER TO DATE INDICATOR *****/
IF(
    MOD(MONTH(Close_Date__c)-1, 3) < MOD(MONTH(TODAY())-1, 3)
    ||
    (
        MOD(MONTH(Close_Date__c)-1, 3) = MOD(MONTH(TODAY())-1, 3)
        &&
        DAY(Close_Date__c) <= DAY(TODAY())
    ),
    "TD",
    ""
)
&
"|" /***** MONTH OFFSET CALCULATION *****/
&
TEXT(
    MONTH(Close_Date__c) - MONTH(TODAY())
    +
    12 * (YEAR(Close_Date__c) - YEAR(TODAY()))
)
&
"M"
& /***** MONTH TO DATE INDICATOR *****/
IF( DAY(Close_Date__c) <= DAY(TODAY()),
    "TD",
    ""
)
&
"|" /***** WEEK OFFSET CALCULATION *****/
&
TEXT(
    (
        (Close_Date__c- WEEKDAY(Close_Date__c))
        -
        (TODAY() - WEEKDAY(TODAY()))
    )
    /
    7
)
&
"W"
& /***** WEEK TO DATE INDICATOR *****/
IF(WEEKDAY(Close_Date__c) <= WEEKDAY(TODAY()),
    "TD",
    ""
)
&
"|" /***** DAY OFFSET CALCULATION *****/
&
TEXT(
    Close_Date__c - TODAY()
)
&
"D"
&
"|"
fields.label: Close Date YoY
fields.name: Close_Date_YoY__c
